<plot>In a mountainous town in the State of Ceará, Brazil, Ajax soccer team kids play a game to see who will win the heart of romantic Salma, sister of one of the players, and the coach's daughter, a Lebanese owner of Casa Beirute. Salma promises to choose one of the boys, after an important game, which is tragically interrupted by an accident. Twenty years later, still alone, she promotes a new game, and finds out the reason of such a long and painful indecision.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268393</url></doc>
